com.github.jonathanxd.iutils.box

Interface UnknownBox<T>

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    BaseBox<T>, IMutableBox<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BooleanBox, ByteBox, CharBox, DoubleBox, FloatBox, ImmutableBox, IntBox, LongBox, MutableBox, ShortBox

    public interface UnknownBox<T>
    Box that has only getter and setter link methods. Methods to implement (required): type() get() void set(type() value) This is base class of all boxes, it includes primitive boxes.
